    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly, providing reliable performance, and the transmission shifts cleanly through all gears. While the exterior shows some minor signs of regular use, such as small stone chips and light surface scratches, the paint still holds a nice shine. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner.",
