    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the high-revving S54 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal power delivery. Significant mechanical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The suspension maintains its factory kinematics for a balanced, communicative chassis, while the braking system retains excellent thermal capacity. This is a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car optimized for performance and structural longevity.",
